---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About Us" description="Learn about CodesCompiler's mission to provide free web development education.">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto py-12 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-white shadow-sm my-8 rounded-lg">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-6">About CodesCompiler</h1>
    <div class="prose prose-brand prose-lg">
      <p>Welcome to <strong>CodesCompiler.com</strong>. Our mission is to make web development education accessible, straightforward, and entirely free for everyone around the world.</p>
      
      <h2>Our Vision</h2>
      <p>We believe that anyone with an internet connection should have the opportunity to learn how to code. Similar to industry standards like W3Schools, we aim to provide comprehensive, easy-to-understand tutorials for core web technologies.</p>

      <h2>What We Offer</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Interactive Learning:</strong> Our "Try It Yourself" editor allows you to write HTML, CSS, and JavaScript and see the results instantly.</li>
        <li><strong>Structured Paths:</strong> We organize content logically from beginner to advanced topics.</li>
        <li><strong>Free Access:</strong> We support our platform through non-intrusive advertisements, ensuring the content remains free forever.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Contact Information</h2>
      <p>For inquiries, please visit our <a href="/contact">Contact Page</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
